{
  "texts": [
    "The colors depict the different clusters of cited references included in the analysis.",
    "References within a cluster are more likely to be cited along with other references from the same cluster (van Eck and Waltman 2022).",
    "Three clusters can be distinguished:",
    "• Cluster I (green) is named \"Foundations of the Metaverse\".",
    "It is composed by three publications about the pillars or fundamental parts upon which the Metaverse should be built."
  ]
}